OL,6,FElaine Wilcox has been at the inquest
OL,7,Finto Charlie Millers' death.
OL,9,FThe mother of a transgender teenager
OL,10,F"pleaded" with social workers for more
OL,11,Fsupport before his death, an inquest
OL,12,Fhas heard.
OL,14,FCharlie Millers, 17, died five days
OL,15,Fafter being found unresponsive in his
OL,16,Froom atHospital near as a result of
OL,17,Fself-inflicted injuries on 2 December
OL,18,F2020.
