OL,3,CMother 'pleaded' for more support
OL,4,Cbefore son's death, inquest hears
OL,6,FWhen asked by the coroner if someone
OL,7,Fwith more experience would have been
OL,8,Fbetter suited to Charlie's care, she
OL,9,Fagreed.
OL,11,FThe 17-year-old from was born female,
OL,12,Fand was severely bullied at school
OL,13,Fwhen he transitioned as a 12-year-old.
OL,14,FHe also claimed he had been sexually
OL,15,Fabused by his peers.
OL,17,FAt the beginning of the inquest
OL,18,FCharlie's mum, Sam Millers, said her
OL,19,Fson had a long history of mental
OL,20,Fhealth issues and regularly self-
OL,21,Fharmed.
