OL,4,Cbefore son's death, inquest hears
OL,6,FHe was sectioned various times, was
OL,7,Fknown to social services and by 2020
OL,8,Fhe was in a cycle of self harming
OL,9,Fbehaviour.
OL,11,FThe inquest was told that Charlie's
OL,12,Fself harming got worse after his
OL,13,Fadmission to the secure ward Junction
OL,14,F17 at Prestwich Hospital.
OL,16,FGiving more evidence, Charlie's mum
OL,17,Ftold the inquest she was working full
OL,18,Ftime and had two other children at
OL,19,Fhome.
