OL,3,CMother 'pleaded' for more support
OL,4,Cbefore son's death, inquest hears
OL,6,FShe had pleaded with social workers
OL,7,Ffor more support and said she often
OL,8,Ffelt like running away.
OL,10,FUnder the Carers Act - extra support
OL,11,Fcould have been given to the family
OL,12,Fbut his social worker was not aware of
OL,13,Fthat this was an option.
OL,15,FShe told the inquest this route was
OL,16,Fnot suggested by her supervisors, who
OL,17,Fwill be giving evidence on Thursday 11
OL,18,FApril.
