OL,3,CMother 'pleaded' for more support
OL,4,Cbefore son's death, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe inquest also heard how before his
OL,7,Fdeath Charlie told his mother that a
OL,8,Fmember of staff on the ward had
OL,9,Fhandled him roughly, called him stupid
OL,10,Fand told him to 'man up' when he was
OL,11,Fself harming.
OL,13,FA month before his death, a social
OL,14,Fworker at the unit reported that staff
OL,15,Fhad watched the 17-year-old self
OL,16,Fharming and did not stop him.
OL,18,FHis injuries were so severe a blood
OL,19,Ftransfusion was considered.
