OL,4,Cbefore son's death, inquest hears
OL,6,FOn the first day of the inquest, his
OL,7,Fmother told the court she had had a
OL,8,Fconversation with him before his death
OL,9,Fwhere he had said he was not doing it
OL,10,Fbecause he wanted to end his life, it
OL,11,Fwas just his way of self-harming.
OL,13,FThe inquest will also examine the
OL,14,Fcircumstances and care provided by
OL,15,FGreater Manchester Mental Health NHS
OL,16,FFoundation Trust, Trafford Borough
OL,17,FCouncil and five other Interested
OL,18,FPersons.
